# About Installation


```sh
composer install
```

```sh
Update .env
```

`Or`

```sh
File name changed .env.example
Check the file permissions of the `.env`
```

### Running file index.php

| Public                             | /                                 |
| ---------------------------------- | --------------------------------- |
| no update                          | need to update                    |
| Only change document root [Cpanel] | copy all files folder public to / |
| ...                                | change path files.                |

##### check if exists file .htaccess

